  "title": "Lit on fire",
  "description": "A simple mod that allow to lit up campfires using torches",
  "body": "<p><img src=\"https://cf.way2muchnoise.eu/versions/1154134.svg\" alt=\"title\" /></p>\n<div><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Forge-blue?style=plastic&amp;link=https%3A%2F%2Ffiles.minecraftforge.net%2Fnet%2Fminecraftforge%2Fforge%2F\" alt=\"Static Badge\" />&nbsp;<img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/NeoForge-lime?style=plastic&amp;link=https%3A%2F%2Fneoforged.net%2F\" alt=\"Static Badge\" /></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">&nbsp;A simple mod that allow to lit up campfires using torches</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://github.com/DevDyna/ContentArchive/blob/main/Lit%20On%20Fire/gif.gif?raw=true\" alt=\"\" width=\"873\" height=\"720\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong>Flint&amp;Steel vs Torches</strong></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">If you want to lit up a campfire you require to clean some space around it</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong>Compatibility/customization</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">This mod allow you to add your own campfire lighter using an itemtag</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Also you can tweak everything from configs</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
